    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049650/extras/8c03c90eda2dc3d38dbe06bc2f1ab3ac.poster.avif?t=1737196927\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049650/extras/8c03c90eda2dc3d38dbe06bc2f1ab3ac.webm?t=1737196927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049650/extras/8c03c90eda2dc3d38dbe06bc2f1ab3ac.mp4?t=1737196927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>HARD2KILL — a hurricane-paced action that combines dynamic platforming with strategic enemy elimination. Leap across arenas, each demanding the extermination of all foes in a precise order to solve combat puzzles. In this game of deadly precision, a single hit means death for you and your enemies. Navigate from one high-stakes arena to the next, where your survival hinges on killing efficiently. HARD2KILL tests your reflexes and tactical prowess in equal measure, offering a pulse-pounding blend of action and strategy.   <br> <br><i>GAME IN EARLY DEVELOPMENT STAGE</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Gain abilities by slaying the enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049650/extras/3bd6b06ea0ffe6964d147c6f2ea8d65c.poster.avif?t=1737196927\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049650/extras/3bd6b06ea0ffe6964d147c6f2ea8d65c.webm?t=1737196927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049650/extras/3bd6b06ea0ffe6964d147c6f2ea8d65c.mp4?t=1737196927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>• Stun and then kill the enemy to gain a unique attack.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049650/extras/11445db0a079c19a724207181e8956f3.poster.avif?t=1737196927\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049650/extras/11445db0a079c19a724207181e8956f3.webm?t=1737196927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049650/extras/11445db0a079c19a724207181e8956f3.mp4?t=1737196927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Choose your next target wisely. Think fast, and move even faster.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049650/extras/6d1032f9a8683abcc5a39b25600ea680.poster.avif?t=1737196927\" width=800 height=478 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049650/extras/6d1032f9a8683abcc5a39b25600ea680.webm?t=1737196927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049650/extras/6d1032f9a8683abcc5a39b25600ea680.mp4?t=1737196927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
